@base = http://localhost:5211
@accessToken = YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

### Health (no auth)
GET {{base}}/health/live
Accept: application/json

###
GET {{base}}/health/ready
Accept: application/json

###

### Register
POST {{base}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "Password123!"
}

###

### Login (copy accessToken from response for below)
# @name login
POST {{base}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@platform.local",
  "password": "Admin123!"
}

###

### Me (use token from login)
GET {{base}}/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Logout (cookie cleared by server)
POST {{base}}/api/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### --- Admin (requires admin role) ---

### Admin – Users list
GET {{base}}/api/admin/users?page=1&pageSize=20
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Admin – Users search
GET {{base}}/api/admin/users?search=admin&page=1&pageSize=20
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Admin – User by id (replace {id} with user Guid)
GET {{base}}/api/admin/users/{id}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Admin – Revoke all refresh tokens for user (replace {id})
POST {{base}}/api/admin/users/{id}/revoke-refresh-tokens
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Admin – Security events
GET {{base}}/api/admin/security-events?page=1&pageSize=50
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Admin – Security events by type
GET {{base}}/api/admin/security-events?type=LOGIN_FAIL&page=1&pageSize=50
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Admin – Health ready
GET {{base}}/api/admin/health/ready
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Admin – Health live
GET {{base}}/api/admin/health/live
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Admin – Version
GET {{base}}/api/admin/version
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

###
